item.title: Elevate Your Normal
item.description: I'm...a guy who one-shots his coffee before it even cools down. -Â Psy, Gangnam Style I recently began running in the snow wearing only a t-shirt, light pants, and my minimalist shoes. Air temperatures here in Boulder have been 34 degrees at the warmest, and down around 23 this morning. Every morning, I look wistfully at my warm hoodie and gloves as I pull on my thin shirt and head out the door.
